text: Vietnascincus is a genus of skinks. It contains one species, Vietnascincus rugosus, which is endemic to Vietnam. ==References== Category:Skinks Category:Monotypic lizard genera Category:Reptiles of Vietnam Category:Endemic fauna of Vietnam Category:Taxa named by Ilya Darevsky Category:Taxa named by Nikolai Loutseranovitch Orlov
title: Vietnascincus
